        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 4. Morphological characters of Hemicrepidius and select genera. Dipropus: a) Head, anterior view; c) Pronotum, lateral view. H. memnonius: b) Head, anterior view; h) Pronotum, dorsal view. Athous instabilis: d) Pronotum, dorsal view; g) Tarsus, lateral view. A. vittatus: e) Tarsus, dorsal view; f) Tarsus, lateral view. Images not to scale. asn = antescutellar notch; fc = frontal carina; fcr = frontoclypeal region; hac = hind angle carina; il = impunctate line; lat = lateral area of pronotum; lpc = lateral pronotal carina; pd = pronotal disc; sln = sublateral notch." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4906777/files/figure.png" .

